,
"info"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"View detailed calendar information for a specified date, defaulting to the current day.\n\nFields provided: date, lunar_date, lunar_daycount, jianchu (值星), weekday,\nbazi (干支), jieqi (节气), jieqi_next, holiday, xiuxi (休/工), yi (宜), ji (忌)\n"
,
"cn"
:
"查看指定日期的详细日历信息，默认为当日。\n\n提供字段：日期、农历、农历月大小、值星、星期、干支、节气、下个节气、假日、休息/工作、宜、忌\n"
}
,
