}
}
}
,
"ls"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"List calendar data in various formats (day/week/month/year view).\n\nData provided:\n- Day/Month view: date, lunar_date, jianchu (值星), weekday, jieqi, xiuxi (休/工), yi (宜), ji (忌), holiday\n- Month summary: year_month, jieqi_list, tiaoxiu_xiu (放假), tiaoxiu_gong (上班)\n- Year view: year, xuanyuan, shengxiao, leap_months, chunjie, qingming, duanwu, zhongqiu\n"
,
"cn"
:
"以多种格式列出日历数据（按日/周/月/年查看）。\n\n提供的数据：\n- 日/月视图: 日期、农历、值星、星期、节气、休息/工作(休/工)、宜、忌、假日\n- 月汇总: 年月、节气列表、调休放假、调休上班\n- 年视图: 生肖、闰月、春节、清明、端午、中秋\n"
}
,
